1
00:01:09,959 --> 00:01:10,920
Don't tell Jiang Yue

2
00:01:12,239 --> 00:01:13,519
what happened last night.

3
00:01:14,400 --> 00:01:14,920
Brother,

4
00:01:15,400 --> 00:01:17,200
are you afraid she'll seek revenge on Qin Yeren?

5
00:01:18,159 --> 00:01:19,200
It's not that simple.

6
00:01:21,239 --> 00:01:22,079
If she goes, she goes.

7
00:01:22,519 --> 00:01:23,560
With her current strength,

8
00:01:23,719 --> 00:01:24,920
she might actually win.

9
00:01:25,280 --> 00:01:26,280
Shut up.

10
00:01:50,159 --> 00:01:50,599
Who's there?

11
00:01:56,319 --> 00:01:57,000
A Che,

12
00:01:58,879 --> 00:02:00,599
you're so quiet every day.

13
00:02:00,840 --> 00:02:02,000
you must be up to something.

14
00:02:02,519 --> 00:02:03,719
Tell me, what are you going to do?

15
00:02:08,400 --> 00:02:09,240
Just passing by.

16
00:02:10,120 --> 00:02:10,599
Stop.

17
00:02:12,360 --> 00:02:14,120
I got hurt because you took me

18
00:02:14,199 --> 00:02:14,960
to meet Qin Yaxin.

19
00:02:15,560 --> 00:02:17,120
Who knew you'd be causing trouble everywhere,

20
00:02:17,439 --> 00:02:18,439
and someone even tried to kill you?

21
00:02:19,280 --> 00:02:20,240
I'll take responsibility for my actions.

22
00:02:20,759 --> 00:02:22,120
I'll accept any punishment my brother gives me.

23
00:02:22,919 --> 00:02:24,360
But I will never apologize to you.

24
00:02:28,680 --> 00:02:29,759
Do you really dislike me that much?

25
00:02:30,080 --> 00:02:31,120
I don't hate you,

26
00:02:31,960 --> 00:02:33,240
but Li Feiyuan.

27
00:02:36,479 --> 00:02:37,439
Lu Zhiyu said

28
00:02:38,159 --> 00:02:40,240
you split up many years ago

29
00:02:40,960 --> 00:02:42,120
because of her.

30
00:02:43,759 --> 00:02:45,000
You really don't know anything?

31
00:02:49,599 --> 00:02:50,639
When we were little,

32
00:02:51,560 --> 00:02:52,759
our parents were kidnapped by the Iron Cage.

33
00:02:53,680 --> 00:02:54,479
My brother went after them

34
00:02:55,120 --> 00:02:56,199
but never came back.

35
00:02:57,360 --> 00:02:58,120
So,

36
00:02:59,120 --> 00:03:00,520
you became an orphan like that.

37
00:03:01,360 --> 00:03:02,199
In the Wolf Clan,

38
00:03:02,719 --> 00:03:04,400
if the alpha wolf is defeated or dies,

39
00:03:04,960 --> 00:03:06,360
his children will be bullied.

40
00:03:06,879 --> 00:03:08,159
I barely survived and grew up.

41
00:03:08,919 --> 00:03:10,199
With great difficulty, I found the Li residence,

42
00:03:10,759 --> 00:03:12,639
only to see my long-lost brother

43
00:03:13,719 --> 00:03:15,439
working as a servant for my enemy.

44
00:03:17,759 --> 00:03:19,159
I found Li Feiyuan in the suburbs,

45
00:03:20,080 --> 00:03:21,159
but he tried to stop me

46
00:03:22,280 --> 00:03:23,560
and pointed his sword at me.

47
00:03:26,840 --> 00:03:28,960
Getting close to humans makes you stupid and ruthless.

48
00:03:30,479 --> 00:03:31,280
Jiang Yue,

49
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:33,479
Your existence is the original sin.

50
00:03:36,439 --> 00:03:37,719
You can think of me however you want.

51
00:03:39,479 --> 00:03:40,319
But your brother,

52
00:03:42,039 --> 00:03:43,280
he really cares about you.

53
00:03:45,159 --> 00:03:46,400
Who cares if he does?

54
00:03:48,080 --> 00:03:50,000
Aren't you coming back to find him

55
00:03:50,199 --> 00:03:51,479
because you're worried about him,

56
00:03:51,639 --> 00:03:52,439
risking being punished?

57
00:03:55,039 --> 00:03:55,439
Forget it.

58
00:03:56,000 --> 00:03:57,840
I'll keep it a secret for you this time.

59
00:03:58,879 --> 00:04:00,120
But if next time,

60
00:04:00,599 --> 00:04:02,439
you dare to be an insider threat again,

61
00:04:03,479 --> 00:04:05,520
I'll teach you a lesson.

62
00:04:09,120 --> 00:04:09,840
Be careful.

63
00:04:25,399 --> 00:04:26,560
Why didn't you sleep in?

64
00:04:27,720 --> 00:04:29,519
You didn't come back all night.

65
00:04:30,000 --> 00:04:31,240
Zhang San and Li Si are not here either.

66
00:04:32,759 --> 00:04:33,959
I took them hunting.

67
00:04:35,279 --> 00:04:37,519
I thought you went to fight again.

68
00:04:37,839 --> 00:04:38,480
No.

69
00:04:43,519 --> 00:04:44,639
The Night of the Full Moon is coming.

70
00:04:45,639 --> 00:04:47,319
I asked the clan to be on a curfew.

71
00:04:47,920 --> 00:04:50,120
We can't let those terrible things happen again.

72
00:04:56,000 --> 00:04:56,639
Are you worried about me?

73
00:04:59,079 --> 00:05:00,199
I'm just thinking that

74
00:05:00,680 --> 00:05:02,560
to live in peace with humans,

75
00:05:02,759 --> 00:05:03,680
you have to hide your identity

76
00:05:03,959 --> 00:05:05,439
and hide on the night of the full moon.

77
00:05:06,120 --> 00:05:07,040
What if

78
00:05:07,199 --> 00:05:08,160
Qin Yeren and his men

79
00:05:08,319 --> 00:05:09,560
take advantage of the situation?

80
00:05:12,519 --> 00:05:14,600
They don't know how dangerous our den is.

81
00:05:22,800 --> 00:05:23,680
I know what you mean.

82
00:05:24,279 --> 00:05:25,439
You mean

83
00:05:25,720 --> 00:05:26,800
Qin Yeren's men

84
00:05:26,959 --> 00:05:29,240
are just ordinary people for a living.

85
00:05:30,319 --> 00:05:31,879
Instead of fighting,

86
00:05:33,000 --> 00:05:33,959
we should

87
00:05:34,600 --> 00:05:36,319
find the evidence

88
00:05:37,040 --> 00:05:38,120
to eradicate him.

89
00:05:42,759 --> 00:05:43,639
I'll tell my brother

90
00:05:43,920 --> 00:05:45,360
to stop doing business

91
00:05:45,879 --> 00:05:47,800
with Qin Yeren.

92
00:05:48,040 --> 00:05:49,199
Or I'll break up with him.

93
00:05:54,399 --> 00:05:55,079
You'd better

94
00:05:55,759 --> 00:05:57,560
keep your relationship

95
00:05:57,759 --> 00:05:58,879
with him.

96
00:06:00,600 --> 00:06:01,879
Or I'll beat him up.

97
00:06:06,040 --> 00:06:06,920
You...

98
00:06:07,480 --> 00:06:08,879
Is it because my brother

99
00:06:08,959 --> 00:06:10,759
is going to give me a galaxy ring

100
00:06:11,800 --> 00:06:13,560
that you want to show me the real galaxy?

101
00:06:15,600 --> 00:06:16,800
You want the ring more?

102
00:06:20,040 --> 00:06:20,600
Then...

103
00:06:21,480 --> 00:06:21,920
Let's go.

104
00:06:23,399 --> 00:06:23,920
Where are we going?

105
00:06:25,560 --> 00:06:26,560
To pick out a ring.

106
00:06:35,240 --> 00:06:37,680
These treasures should be in the gallery.

107
00:06:38,639 --> 00:06:39,920
You just leave them here like this?

108
00:06:41,120 --> 00:06:41,839
There are too many.

109
00:06:42,480 --> 00:06:43,000
They take up space.

110
00:06:44,120 --> 00:06:45,399
Versailles.

111
00:06:46,240 --> 00:06:47,120
There are items from Versailles.

112
00:06:49,120 --> 00:06:51,560
The necklace of Queen Marie of the Bourbon Dynasty.

113
00:06:52,240 --> 00:06:52,920
At that time,

114
00:06:53,439 --> 00:06:54,160
it was called

115
00:06:54,560 --> 00:06:57,160
a glorious gift for vain humans.

116
00:06:58,600 --> 00:06:59,519
So these

117
00:07:00,160 --> 00:07:02,519
are gifts from humans to the vain Wolf King.

118
00:07:03,519 --> 00:07:06,240
These are all souvenirs given by friends at the time.

119
00:07:06,639 --> 00:07:07,600
They are also local specialties.

120
00:07:12,160 --> 00:07:13,480
At that time, they wanted to give me a title.

121
00:07:13,839 --> 00:07:15,279
But I couldn't get used to the food there,

122
00:07:16,000 --> 00:07:16,759
so I resigned.

123
00:07:24,839 --> 00:07:26,680
The coronation of the African chieftain.

124
00:07:32,240 --> 00:07:33,959
Didn't they want to marry their daughter to you?

125
00:07:35,399 --> 00:07:37,199
So I fled overnight.

126
00:07:37,439 --> 00:07:38,279
I remember at that time,

127
00:07:38,800 --> 00:07:40,040
I was also chased by a group of elephants.

128
00:07:43,360 --> 00:07:44,079
Is there anything you like?

129
00:07:46,959 --> 00:07:47,560
No need.

130
00:07:49,480 --> 00:07:51,800
Compared to these artificially carved gems,

131
00:07:52,600 --> 00:07:54,240
I prefer the real galaxy.

132
00:07:54,800 --> 00:07:55,480
Galaxy.

133
00:07:58,600 --> 00:07:59,720
Then you should like this.

134
00:08:02,160 --> 00:08:02,879
Moonstone.

135
00:08:05,720 --> 00:08:06,839
In the eyes of the Romans,

136
00:08:07,360 --> 00:08:09,680
this is a symbol of the essence of the moon.

137
00:08:10,360 --> 00:08:11,079
It is also called

138
00:08:12,199 --> 00:08:13,480
the gift of the moon.

139
00:08:16,920 --> 00:08:17,399
Thanks.

140
00:08:31,920 --> 00:08:32,759
Am I drunk

141
00:08:33,679 --> 00:08:34,679
or dizzy?

142
00:08:50,000 --> 00:08:51,519
Legend has it that the Coyote Clan

143
00:08:52,399 --> 00:08:54,600
has a strong gene brought by the meteorite.

144
00:08:58,320 --> 00:08:59,279
The Wolf Clan

145
00:09:08,919 --> 00:09:12,759
as the supreme god in charge of the sun, live in the mountains and forests.

146
00:09:14,559 --> 00:09:15,799
Nonsense.

147
00:09:37,240 --> 00:09:39,600
A'ren Fisherman's Seafood Stall.

148
00:11:17,480 --> 00:11:18,440
Coach, please evaluate.

149
00:11:20,840 --> 00:11:21,559
Very flexible.

150
00:11:22,759 --> 00:11:23,320
As for strength,

151
00:11:25,200 --> 00:11:26,240
you need to eat a little more.

152
00:11:26,480 --> 00:11:27,080
Then in the future,

153
00:11:27,159 --> 00:11:28,200
when you go out to fight,

154
00:11:28,279 --> 00:11:29,320
I can also be a helper.

155
00:11:29,440 --> 00:11:30,080
No way.

156
00:11:30,200 --> 00:11:32,120
You are easily seen as a target by others,

157
00:11:32,279 --> 00:11:33,440
and take you back to their den

158
00:11:33,679 --> 00:11:34,320
to eat.

159
00:11:34,799 --> 00:11:35,840
It's not that easy.

160
00:11:44,279 --> 00:11:46,519
You were just yelling about eating me,

161
00:11:47,080 --> 00:11:48,759
and now you're gone.

162
00:12:10,480 --> 00:12:11,200
The old one is broken.

163
00:12:12,960 --> 00:12:14,720
Just finished boxing, my arm's sore.

164
00:12:46,759 --> 00:12:47,519
Is the brand

165
00:12:48,120 --> 00:12:49,559
fading away?

166
00:12:52,720 --> 00:12:53,879
I want to bite you again

167
00:12:55,559 --> 00:12:56,480
to keep you from leaving.

168
00:13:00,039 --> 00:13:01,240
I'm immune to it.

169
00:13:01,840 --> 00:13:02,919
One bite won't be enough.
